{"tid":1384941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人應該要勇武定係和理非？","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:46:45.000Z","uid":291448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edf3e849fec4c06c76235d779c45838566d0a52d","tid":1384941,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"呢個反修例運動我由6月9號開始就一直關注到而家 最初我覺得只要和理非 和平遊行應該好快呢件事就會平息啦 點知最終只係換黎林鄭嘅一句<span style=\"color: red;\">暫緩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時D黑警打人打得越嚟越過分 催淚彈係咁放  橡膠子彈係咁射 仲要仆街到射頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經完全唔係香港警察嚟  最近就直頭勾結埋黑社會 打極999都冇警察黎 任由市民俾人打到爆曬缸 冇幾耐之後就到班畜龍小隊暴打市民  所以我覺得而家香港人必要時一定要勇武抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔可以再繼續和理非 淨係識得和理非D黑警只會打得你更加大力  <br />\n最後都係果句 <span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命 光復香港</span> 香港人加油🇭🇰  期待呢場運動成功嘅一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdHQYZf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdHQYZf.png&h=2e0c3cec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgXUGcB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgXUGcB.png&h=6e129de3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ef4ce39af27d2d44737ddd5d35e94a233443313","tid":1384941,"uid":89184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"both!!!"},{"pid":"6becfd76b0b61751aa35c885385edde1159617bd","tid":1384941,"uid":54472,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係要2選1 知進退 識變通 適當時候用適當手段</span></span>"},{"pid":"9cd01af757240f4dfd9a8914f11a2b441efce3b8","tid":1384941,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6becfd76b0b61751aa35c885